storyInfo:
Blaze and FrostNova are evenly matched, but the building collapses in the aftermath of the battle. The Doctor and Frostnova both tumble into the void.
Rhodes Island strikes a temporary truce with the Yeti Squadron.

attributes.content: I'm fine! They... have some moves.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Thanks to you, we're okay. You're keeping the air warm enough to stop her chills.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Hey Frosty, why aren't you using lethal Arts?
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Get out of here, Amiya. There could be more Reunion on the way. Do we have any injured? I can help.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: I'm going to politely suggest that you don't fight anymore, snow bunny.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: If you keep using your Arts like that, you're going to die. You're just burning your life into power.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Or, you could always come to Rhodes Island. We've got ways to extend your life.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Don't look at me like that... I don't need your pity.
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: Do I look like I pity you? You're strong. I respect you.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Dr. {@nickname}, run. Don't look at her!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Reunion forces closing on our position!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Sister, don't use that now, not where you're standing!
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: Who knows what Rhodes Island might do to our people in Lungmen!
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: The temperature difference... it's causing the structure... to weaken!
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: The Originium we buried has changed the structure of the lower levels, the plates are tilting!
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: Sister, it's too dangerous! Hold onto me!
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: Is that the sound of the structure shattering?
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Buried Originium... heat absorption... temperature difference...
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: It's collapsing... FrostNova's Arts can actually do that...?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Reunion is capable of something like this?
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: All I know is... the whole district is sinking!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Run! Get to a stable area! The ground here is caving in!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Doctor, the ground under you... it's... splitting?
attributes.name: Jessica

attributes.content: Amiya, stay where you are! Dr. {@nickname}, grab onto that lamppost!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: The ground is splitting too fast! I can't reach!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: The buildings can't support their own weight anymore, they're all collapsing!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Amiya, go. I'll get the Doctor! I'm an elite operator, I can do it!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Welp, looks like we're not quite done.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Doctor, I'm going to use airflow and pressure to slow your fall and push away the building beside you. Don't worry, it won't crush you!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Just don't panic! I've got you!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Your commander fell down there too, huh?
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Rabbit of Rhodes Island, could we forge a temporary armistice? Honestly, we never much wanted to fight you.
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: Mephisto told our sister you'd killed Alex, and she was very concerned about what you would do next.
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: I'm sorry. I did kill Skullshatterer.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Infected really should not fight one another. I'm sorry.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: What's to apologize for? It was a battle, wasn't it?
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: So let's have a ceasefire. Nesti, what do you say?
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: Nesti says he's fine with it.
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: I don't think that's what he said.
attributes.name: Frostleaf

attributes.content: As long as we're not in battle, there's no reason to kill anyone, right?
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: Why is it... you want a ceasefire?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Did you ever notice that both our sides are led by rabbits?
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: I think something in my brain just broke.
attributes.name: Frostleaf

attributes.content: These are the yetis of the ice field?
attributes.name: Frostleaf

attributes.content: Shouldn't they be cold, merciless killers?
attributes.name: Frostleaf

attributes.content: Who wins the battle, or where you go, none of that matters to us. All we care about is our sister's life.
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: And you're worried about your friend too, right?
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: ...Right. We didn't come here to hurt anyone.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: You're definitely not here to hunt Reunion for sport, are you?
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: If it weren't for Patriot insisting on unity in the Reunion Movement, we'd have dealt with Mephisto and his people a long time ago.
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member

attributes.content: And that'd be kinda like hunting Reunion for sport, huh?
attributes.name: Yeti Squad Member
